description: Recently sold: $103,000. Beautiful country home, completely remodeled in 2009. New windows, roof siding, paint, flooring, electrical, and the list goes on. In the basement you have a huge family room along with another room which can be used as a fourth bedroom or office (no egress) and also a gorgeous bathroom with double sinks and shower. Outside, you have a wonderful deck to relax on while you admire your beautiful front and backyard. Also a super large 6 stall garage. Enough room for the snowmobiles, boats and four wheelers. Close to Giants Ridge Ski and Golf Resort, snowmobile and four wheeler trails. Easy access to Tower, Babbitt, Aurora & Virginia with no dirt roads. This one is a must see!

Recently sold: $50,000. Cute and cozy 2br/2ba country home on over 3.5 acres. Beautiful setting, even a tree house! Inside you have warm maple cabinetry and original hardwood floors which opens to a large spacious living room / dining room combined. Walk thru the French doors and you have another bedroom, or office if you prefer with a 1/4 bath and main floor laundry! Upstairs you have two bedrooms and a spa like bathroom, complete with claw foot tub! Dry basement ready to be finished out for even more inside living space. Brokered And Advertised By: Z' Up North Realty Listing Agent: Andrea Zupancich
